name: Sonification 06 - polygonal drones
description:
Track six (of six) from the album "Sonification"  - an experimental electronic/industrial crossover album created from a mix of programmed sounds, noises and improvised electronics.  - 320kbps mp3 format. 
"Sonification" is written, arranged, programmed, and performed by Craig L. Saunders
Trk 1, 2, 3, 5: Co-written, with additional programming and performance by ToMsLuG.
Trk 6: additional programming by ToMsluG. 
Produced by Craig L. Saunders and ToMsLuG
